<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1245</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 bā shān shān shì shén de shān, shì duō fēng duō lǐng de shān.
 nǐ men duō fēng duō lǐng de shān wèi hé xié kàn,
 shén suǒ yuàn jū zhù de shān, shén suǒ yuàn jū zhù de shān.
 yé hé huá bì zhù zhè shān zhí dào yǒng yuǎn. zhí dào yǒng yuǎn.
 shén de chē niǎn lèi wàn yíng qiān, zhǔ zài qí zhōng hǎo xiàng zài xī nǎi shān.
 tā lǔ lüè chóu dí yǐ jīng shēng shàng gāo tiān, zhí zhǎng wáng quán dào yǒng yuǎn.
 wǒ men yào xiàng zhǔ huān hū, wǒ men yào xiàng zhǔ sòng zàn.
 yīn tā yǔ wǒ men tóng zài, zhè lǐ shì tā de shèng shān.</lyrics>
<title>bā shān shān shì shén de shān 迦南1245</title>
</song>